data.description: DON'T MISS OUT on this completely updated, gorgeous home in popular Kearney neighborhood! MOVE-IN READY! Home is in immaculate condition and offers a ton of great space with a lot of natural light, new carpet and interior paint throughout! Walk into the spacious entry with high ceilings and a very open floor plan. Main level has a beautiful large eat-in kitchen with gorgeous hardwood floors and plenty of counter-top space. Kitchen opens to a family room with vaulted ceilings and a beautiful fireplace. Main level also has 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a laundry area. Additional space in the finished basement has a large rec room, half bath and walks into a large garage that has been perfectly retrofitted, complete with wet bar area, small refrigerator, heater and tv's, perfect for entertaining! Large covered deck with an extremely private backyard, huge open area with nothing but a field to view. Amazing location, quiet neighborhood! A MUST SEE!
